    {
        "content": "<p>alexcrichton created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12689#discussion_r2865969889\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Hm ok yeah this is going to be a little gnarly, so I've <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12689/changes/5fadc6336eafe62234f295824c804e5ad1a42c7d\">added a test</a> for the current behavior documenting that it's a bit buggy, but it at least preserves the <code>anyhow</code> roundtrip. I'll file a follow-up issue for this.</p>\n</blockquote>",
